snippet.title: Longplay of The Lord of the Rings: Volume 1
snippet.description:
Longplay of The Lord of the Rings: Volume 1, played with the NTSC version on the Super Nintendo Entertainment System. This game's version was released in Oct. 1994. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment below!

0:00:00 - Startup
0:00:44 - Intro
0:05:03 - Hobbiton
0:09:55 - Hobbiton Caves
0:22:32 - Forest of Brandywine
0:48:04 - The Barrow-Downs
1:38:21 - Bree
1:47:41 - Hidden Cave
2:12:16 - The Barrow-Downs (for Yellow Gem)
2:31:00 - Rivendell
2:38:03 - Mines of Moria
3:23:33 - The Balrog
3:27:20 - Ending
3:31:41 - Credits

By: JTBKnuggetsauce
